###Difference between Constructor Vs ngOnInit in Angular

Shortly speaking - use:
- constructor() for Dependency Injection/initializing fields,
- use ngOnInit() for angular component binding.

Sources:
[Quick article with good explanation](https://medium.com/@coderonfleek/constructor-vs-ngoninit-angular-2-components-b1a33db0be65)
